Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相对速度同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:04:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听得到吗  全员集中到中央区域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的话  赶快集中到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时一样  年轻机师的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在排斥佩丽丝少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在分析了桃子的任务记录器后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在少尉的脑量子波检测到了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一般是不可能的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是受到了外部的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外部的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那施加影响的人只可能与少尉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是神经胶质细胞得到加强并使用脑量子波的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和佩丽丝一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机师晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各机  在将长翅膀的回收到4号舰上后  请退回到安全区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊万下士请与本队汇合  并发送撤退信号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这边的死角了  转不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  阿里路亚没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会那么疏忽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长翅膀的收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业员把驾驶员从机体里带出来拘捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业班  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长  不管是哪种方式的X线断层摄像术都出现了错误
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为那种特殊粒子的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4号舰  出发准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于佩丽丝少尉而言  是次不足够的初战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成作战任务  这是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校  有热源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部机体散开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4号舰请紧急离开这个宇宙区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这攻击  是庞然大物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还有别动队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌运输舰中有Kyrios的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被敌人捕获了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罪该万死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校  敌人进入了射击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准了4号舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该知道有自己人在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也要开火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不适合当Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和铁人不一样  新型号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然躲开了两次？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我  请把长翅膀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佩丽丝少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4号舰在指定宇宙域待机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了把机师从长翅膀的里面拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据情况  准许使用切割刀具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,运输舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一台机体  就想同Virtue对抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你捣乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,极近距离的话  即使炮弹被弹开的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你别得意！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的桃子…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校  少尉的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS部队一边支援佩丽丝少尉  一边进行庞然大物捕获作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舰桥  在机体外部没有找到类似开关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要使用切割刀具了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到…声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你捣乱的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了  那时的…女人的声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,运输器内发生异常情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快联络中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中…中校  船体被从内部破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4号舰  出什么事了  赶快报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4号舰的反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是我的判断失误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  可不能空手回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样  都要捕获那庞然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那台机体能感觉到不一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌人开炮后开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可别挂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然小看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早就知道在发射之前会有时间滞后了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发射凝胶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你得逞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中…中校  机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这庞然大物的推进力居然能超过6台铁人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,头部也好  手部也罢  夺一个过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,张开…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吹开了装甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中止作战  从当前宇宙区域撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么早就暴露了Nadleeh的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打乱了计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吠陀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算击溃了7台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就9台了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退信号么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了  逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于撤了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方MS队  开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得…得救了么  我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然在作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快前往回收Kyrios和Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉  机体的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长距离加速虽然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是航行没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用到这么大的规模和人力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连1机都没能捕获到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校  前方有物体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长翅膀的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了  铁人的高机动超兵型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没错  对老子的脑量子波干涉了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是同类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体被到处强化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大脑也被随意摆布而制造出来的怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉  以你的机体的状况的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有胆量啊  女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  在耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  因为是同类  你知道的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请和少尉一起离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校和少尉的能力是顶武所必需的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请记得为我报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你击毁少尉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别来碍事  一般兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是个有生命的东西罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中  中校  请赶快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快撤退  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让男人的觉悟付诸东流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  丢下同伴跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作风一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人革的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天  你们会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们辛苦建立的国家的秩序加以扰乱的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用讲这么冠冕堂皇的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把人改造成士兵的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么秩序可言？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我让那个女人从手心里跑了稍微有些不满
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会轻松的杀掉你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被压倒性的暴力夺走性命却无能为力的感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  求你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来也是个贪生怕死的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,临死前会想起什么呢  妈妈吗  恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:19:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在脑海中正走马灯般浮现出从小到大的景象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  哈里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下哦  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正好是最精彩的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做不到我才这样做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样做！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逗你玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴吧  阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校  明中尉被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都别说了  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么  哈里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么想要那样杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的…本质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不是人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现Virtue了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,显示在显示器上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了Nadleeh么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是  Nadleeh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Kyrios发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚  能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了  这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又…错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是…无可救药了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格所追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam正在体现着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  为什么Meister们这么不完全呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是监视者而非执行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我所能做的就是继续注视着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那是通往毁灭的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,索玛·佩丽丝的存在让阿里路亚决定执行某个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是对于过去的赎罪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「阿里路亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血的洗礼  那是来自背弃神的人的祝福
